F2                              over a word and it modifies the same 
                                words in the file

Ctrl +                          delete to erase a whole line of code

Ctrl + J                        to join lines

Ctrl + Shift + O                to global navigate files by name

Ctrl + P                        go to file by name

Ctrl + Shift + F                to globaly find a word in any file

Ctrl + `                        to open and close the terminal

Select + Ctrl + Shift + L       write in many lines at the same time

Select + Ctrl + D               write in many lines with the same name, 
                                the more you press Ctrl D the more lines 
                                it selects